# Misc
# Ignore .claude by default but share team-wide harness config:
#  - skills/  : project skills (egress-audit, etc.) — picked up by Claude Code
#  - hooks/   : pre/post tool-use scripts (e.g. egress-audit-gate.sh)
#  - settings.json : project-wide hook + permission config
# Per-user overrides (settings.local.json) stay ignored.
.claude/*
!.claude/skills/
!.claude/hooks/
!.claude/settings.json
.claude/settings.local.json
*.bak
*.tmp
.vercel
.env*.local

# Zoom recordings
*.mov
*.mp4
*.avi

# Auto-approve agent
auto-approve-agent/
tsconfig.tsbuildinfo
supabase/.temp/

# Local dev runtime junk (logs, scratch PDF copies)
tmp/
